{"title":"泥土在燃烧","authors":["傅仇"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土在燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傅仇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣红色的烈马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣红色的衣袍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马如流火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣如大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷起热烈的旋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草地上飞跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千个帐篷闻马啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民的儿子回来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民拥来拦烈马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着青年直问好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急如星火的烈马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么好音飞报？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问你勘查草地的工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀中又带来什么珍宝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看马蹄下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的泥土在欢笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请听我的怀里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的泥土在高叫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怀抱千里草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑着烈马飞跑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带来一包泥土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来向乡亲汇报："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请在你们的脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起泥土瞧瞧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们藏族几代牧民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在它上面放牧，睡觉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历来只说草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只长丰盛的牧草；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知草地太富饶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天才认清它的真面貌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑油油的泥土呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它藏着多少火苗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是泥炭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是燃料！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地找到了燃料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地就更兴旺了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们煮茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烤火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将不再烧牛马粪了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐篷里电灯齐明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂里马达欢叫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挤牛奶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制奶粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪羊毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就要用机器了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我们伟大的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫草地又翻身了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我们伟大的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得泥土也燃烧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民翻身上马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着枣红色的烈马；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手举着泥土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起霞光万道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑着烈马飞跃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾的草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里泥土在燃烧！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}